基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 文化藝術素養
 Spirit of Humanism
□ 誠信務實與民主法治
 Civic Concern
□ 環保與社會服務
 Social Concern
□ 全球視野
 Global Vision
 

核心能力 Competence
■ 運用基礎科學理論探究事物本質的能力。(能力一)
 Possess the ability to apply fundamental scientific theory to explore the essence of things.
■ 運用專業工程素養，設計製程單元、整合並組織系統的能力。(能力二)
 Possess the ability to utilize engineering professional, design process units, integrate and organize systems.
□ 設計與執行實驗，以及分析與解釋數據的能力。(能力三)
 Possess the ability to design and execute experiments, and analyze and interpret data.
■ 具備使用現代工具及執行工程實務所需技術、技巧的能力。(能力四)
 Possess the expertise and skill for utilizing modern tools and executing engineering practices.
□ 具備口頭與撰寫報告、有效溝通、領域整合及團隊合作的能力。(能力五)
 Possess the ability to give presentations, write reports, communicate effectively, integrate different fields, and work with others as a team.
■ 發掘、分析、應用研究成果及處理複雜且整合性工程問題的能力。(能力六)
 Possess the ability to discover, analyze, apply research results, and handle complex and integrated engineering problems.
■ 理解及應用專業倫理，認知社會責任及尊重多元觀點 (能力七)
 Apprehend and apply professional ethics, acknowledge societal responsibility, and respect diversified perspectives.
■ 認識時勢變遷，瞭解工程技術對環境、社會及全球的影響，並培養終身學習成長的習慣。(能力八)
 Understand the changes in the modern world, understand the influence of the engineering technology on the environment, society, and earth, and cultivate the habit on lifelong learning.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       儀器分析與分析化學1) Introduction to analytical chemistry, 2) Chemical concepts and Chemical equilibrium, 3) Statistical data in
analysis, 4) Gravimetric methods and Titrations, 5) Introduction to spectrometric methods, 6) Atomic absorption
spectroscopy, 7) Atomic X-ray spectrometry, 8) Ultraviolet and visible absorption spectroscopy, 9) Infrared
spectroscopy, 10) Surface characterization by spectroscopy and microscopy, 11) Introduction to chromatographic
separations, 12) Gas chromatography, 13) Liquid chromatography, 14) Thermal analysis.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    瞭解分析化學與儀器分析原理    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction to instrumental analysis and analytical chemistry2Chemical concepts and Chemical equilibrium3Statistical data in analysis4Gravimetric methods and Titrations5Introduction to spectrometric methods6Mid-term Examination/Optical atomic spectroscopy7Optical atomic spectroscopy/Atomic absorption spectroscopy8Atomic absorption spectroscopy/Atomic X-ray spectrometry9Ultraviolet and visible absorption spectroscopy10Ultraviolet and visible absorption spectroscopy/Infrared spectroscopy11Infrared spectroscopy12Mid-term Examination/Introduction to chromatographic separations13Introduction to chromatographic separations14Gas chromatography15Liquid chromatography16Thermal analysis17Surface characterization by spectroscopy and microscopy18Final Examination 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


